 \; non-member deadline 31 August 2026\; Film Independent member extension 
 to 14 September 2026.\n\nOrganisation: Film Independent\nLocation: Los Ang
 eles\, US\nAward: Lab fellowship + access to bundled $10K fellowships (Cay
 ton-Goldrich\, MPAC\, Sony Music Vision) and Climate Entertainment Develop
 ment Grant ($25K for climate-focused fiction features)\nDuration: Lab coho
 rt\n\nMore: https://www.filmindependent.org/programs/applications/
